1> create a EmployeeRegisterServlet to Register the 
	employee, then show the registration detail and 
	also show login page (using requestDispatcher include()
	method and ask user to login after registration
	eg:
	request	.getRequestDispatcher("/login.html")
		.include(request, response);
	
2>  create a EmployeeLoginServlet to authenticate the 
	employee and dispatch valid user to WelcomeEmployeeServlet
	and invalid user to InvalidEmployeeServlet